THE GAME
--------

  'Passage' is a Workbench game where the idea is to move
horizontally or vertically in each of the game boards, so you can
get to the exit (marked by an hexagonal shape where an 'E' is
displayed). To move, 3 obstacles as well as an empty space must
surround your position. These obstacles can be blocks, gates,
walls as well as one or more of the game board's borders.

  Each game board consists of an area of various size and shape
that contains diagonal gates. Your position, indicated by a
smiling face icon, is located somewhere on the board. On some
boards, walls as well as blocks that are placed here and there,
hinder your movements and complicate the game a little...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

